## Update a package repository

```shell
$ curl 'https://ci.example.com/go/api/admin/repositories/0530f1a9-5282-4b69-be59-066a35076452' \
      -u 'username:password' \
      -H 'Accept: application/vnd.go.cd.v1+json' \
      -H 'If-Match: "26b227605daf6f2d7768c8edaf61b861"' \
      -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
      -X PUT -d '{
        "name" : "npmjs.org",
        "plugin_metadata": {
          "id": "npm",
          "version": "1"
        },
        "configuration": [
          {
            "key": "REPO_URL",
            "value": "http://registry.npmjs.com"
          },
          {
            "key": "USERNAME",
            "value": "admin"
          },
          {
            "key": "PASSWORD",
            "encrypted_value": "aSdiFgRRZ6A="
          }
        ]
      }'
```

